column1:
We celebrate women everyday #internationalwomensday #PressforProgress end but we will keep it going. 

Our message is acronym I.W.D:
I - Inclusion of Women in all Sectors to advance the economy and promote global peace.
w - Women will commit to take actions to accelerate gender parity and empowerment 
D - Discriminate and abuse of Women the girl child, in any forms should be outlawed 
 #IWD2018 #NNEW #TGIF

International Women's Day 
A strong call to #PressforProgress. 
A strong call to unite family, friends, circles, tribes, colleagues and the whole communities to think, act and be gender inclusive.
How will you Press for progress?
When will you Press for Progress?
Where will you Press for progress? 
Take a step, Join us live on our Facebook Page www.facebook.com/nnewomen as we celebrate this occasion.
